tion properties\nin these materials are determined by screening. Finally, the conclusions also\nseem to be of help for the description of the experimental observations of\nmetal-insulator transitions and Mott properties in atoms trapped in planar\nphotonic lattices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2013 21:43:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-12"}
