 downward pumping,\nwe get a more reasonable period and more solar-like behavior even with low\ndiffusivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Sep 2013 14:21:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Feb 2014 18:17:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-05"}
