 moored ULS and on Submarine\n. ESA (ERS1, 2, ENVISAT, CryoSat2), future ESA (Sentinel) and NASA satellite\nand airborne missions, climate and numerical forecast programs will benefit the\nresults of this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Sep 2013 17:09:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-12"}
